<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">今年11月9日</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">是第34个全国消防日</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">国务院安委会办公室、国家消防救援局</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">定于11月份在全国开展消防宣传月活动</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">主题是</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“全民消防、生命至上——安全用火用电”</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为做好消防宣传月各项工作</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">按照国务院安委会办公室、国家消防救援局</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">通知要求</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">各地将组织开展</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">“安全用火用电”系列活动</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032084627.png" alt="1763032084627.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032084627.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032099263.png" alt="1763032099263.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032099263.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032112546.png" alt="1763032112546.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032112546.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032134077.png" alt="1763032134077.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032134077.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032145346.png" alt="1763032145346.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032145346.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032158751.png" alt="1763032158751.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032158751.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032170228.png" alt="1763032170228.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032170228.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032181562.png" alt="1763032181562.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032181562.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032199552.png" alt="1763032199552.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1763032199552.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: right; line-height: 2;">来源：中华人民共和国应急管理部</p>